		<div class="entry-content"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/11/13/today-in-small-business-avoiding-bad-yelp-reviews/" data-title="Today in Small Business: Avoiding Bad Yelp Reviews" data-description="Did this &quot;cereal milk&quot; start-up target the wrong market? Should small businesses have to offer health insurance to part-time workers? The ultimate list of start-up competitions, hackathons, business-plan contests and more.">
