<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Wal-Mart Stores reports that <a href="//www.nytimes.com/reuters/2014/11/13/business/13reuters-walmart-results.html">comparable sales</a> at its American stores rose for the first time in seven quarters.</p>
