<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Americans say <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/11/13/upshot/americans-say-they-want-privacy-but-act-as-if-they-dont.html?partner=rss&amp;emc=rss">they want privacy</a>, but they act as if they donât.</p>
