<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Lyftâs co-founder <a href="//venturebeat.com/2014/11/11/lyfts-cofounder-imagines-a-future-where-strangers-share-driverless-cars/">imagines a future</a> where strangers share driverless cars.</p>
