<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ RadioShack <a href="//www.bizjournals.com/dallas/news/2014/11/12/radioshack-backtracks-on-thanksgiving-plans.html">decides to modify</a> its holiday hours.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A Black Friday line is <a href="//www.washingtontimes.com/news/2014/nov/12/black-friday-line-forming-outside-california-best-/">already forming</a> outside a California Best Buy.</p>
